e medal\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was a little girl from a tiny village,\\\" the 23-year-old said in herinterview, which went viral across social media.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little girl\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"a tiny village\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"herinterview\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still am that little girl from Sligo and I was able to win a medal at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.9999994331825989, \"rank\": 4.3018795232131184e-07, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that little girl\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it just goes to show, you can do anything you set your mind to.\\\"\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"your mind\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From RT\\u00c9 Sport, Mona McSharry wins Ireland's first medal at the Paris Games Her performancemarked Ireland's first medalat the 2024 Games, quickly followed byDaniel Wiffen'ssublimegold in the men's 800m freestyle event.The swimmers are emblematic of an inspiring new wave of talented Irish Olympians who deliver world-class performances and authentically showcase their unique personalities.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"sco