dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"Daniel Wiffen\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games Irish sports fans\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's Olympians\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many now speak witha frank and steely determinationto conquer their sports and openly declare their ambitions to set new world records and win Olympic gold medals.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their sports\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"their ambitions\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"new world records\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bucking the trend of the clich\\u00e9d, boring, robotic sports interview, they are not afraid to be themselves in front of the camera and are not dissuaded from being confident about their desire to win medals and be the best in the world.\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trend\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"the clich\\u00e9d, boring, robotic sports interview\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"the camera\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"their desire\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2628}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a host of European records to their names and a litany of recent medals around their necks, members of Team Ireland have had every reason to be confident in the build-up to Paris, where experts atSports Illustratedpredicteda record haul of Irish medals.\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2783, \"end\": 2795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1112786904313935e-23, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2853, \"end\": 2858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1202218853581974e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9131065603736535, \"rank\": 0.05060067748159111, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a host\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"European records\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"their names\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"a litany\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2732}, {\"ngram\": \"recent medals\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"their necks\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"members\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"every reason\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2815}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"Illustratedpredicteda record haul\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anotable differencein recent Olympics is how this new generation of Irish athletes now speak about themselves, coming across as more assured, ambitious and incredibly authentic in interviews, which often go viral.\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 3146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3003, \"end\": 3008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9131065603736535, \"rank\": 0.05060067748159111, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anotable differencein recent Olympics\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"this new generation\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"interviews\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not coming away without a medal,\\\" Wiffen confidentlystatedahead of the Olympics, before going on to deliver the goods with a historic gold for Ireland.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3298, \"end\": 3305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999990582182, \"rank\": 9.411541651383958e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3184}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3232}, {\"ngram\": \"the goods\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3270}, {\"ngram\": \"a historic gold\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From RT\\u00c9 Sport, Kellie Harrington talks abour her quarter-final win over Angie Valdes Pana at Paris 2024 It is thefun natureof the Olympics that fans tune in to enjoy different sports which they are not experts in, whether that be swimming, rowing, or gymnastics.\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3326, \"end\": 3343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kellie Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"her quarter-final win\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3375}, {\"ngram\": \"Angie Valdes\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3393}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 3402, \"to\": 3407}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3447}, {\"ngram\": \"different sports\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This places an added significance and importance on these television interviews with athletes before and after their events.\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an added significance\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3606}, {\"ngram\": \"importance\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3621}, {\"ngram\": \"these television interviews\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3652}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3666}, {\"ngram\": \"their events\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Such interviews are an important gateway thatbuilds a relationshipbetween the public and an athlete who they might never have seen or even heard of before.\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Such interviews\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3713}, {\"ngram\": \"an important gateway thatbuilds\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3749}, {\"ngram\": \"a relationshipbetween\", \"from\": 3750, \"to\": 3771}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3782}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether on RT\\u00c9, BBC or EuroSport, these TV interviews are especially pivotal in Olympic sports because they convey the significance of what we are watching.\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 4011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3869}, {\"ngram\": \"these TV interviews\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 3908}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic sports\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 3949}, {\"ngram\": \"the significance\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 3986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theyhighlightthe human struggle and sacrifice of the athlete's journey and showcase the joy and despair of winning and losing.\", \"from\": 4012, \"to\": 4138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Theyhighlightthe human struggle\", \"from\": 4012, \"to\": 4043}, {\"ngram\": \"sacrifice\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4057}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's journey\", \"from\": 4061, \"to\": 4082}, {\"ngram\": \"the joy\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4103}, {\"ngram\": \"despair\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We may not be experts in the technicalities of badminton, canoeing or rhythmic gymnastics, but everyone can connect with an Olympic athlete by hearing their story and personality in their own words.\", \"from\": 4139, \"to\": 4337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4160}, {\"ngram\": \"the technicalities\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"badminton\", \"from\": 4186, \"to\": 4195}, {\"ngram\": \"rhythmic gymnastics\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4228}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4242}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic athlete\", \"from\": 4260, \"to\": 4278}, {\"ngram\": \"their story\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4301}, {\"ngram\": \"personality\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4317}, {\"ngram\": \"their own words\", \"from\": 4321, \"to\": 4336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All top-level athletes receive a significant level of media training throughout their careers to manage these media duties.\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All top-level athletes\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4361}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant level\", \"from\": 4370, \"to\": 4389}, {\"ngram\": \"media training\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"their careers\", \"from\": 4419, \"to\": 4432}, {\"ngram\": \"these media duties\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet this often has the detrimental effect of producing boring, robotic interviews where the name of the game is to say as little as possible and not cause controversy.\", \"from\": 4463, \"to\": 4630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the detrimental effect\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4504}, {\"ngram\": \"boring, robotic interviews\", \"from\": 4518, \"to\": 4544}, {\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4559}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4571}, {\"ngram\": \"controversy\", \"from\": 4618, \"to\": 4629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many sports stars stick to a script, keeping their answers as bland and safe as possible, in order to avoid any potential negative publicity.\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many sports stars\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4648}, {\"ngram\": \"a script\", \"from\": 4658, \"to\": 4666}, {\"ngram\": \"their answers\", \"from\": 4676, \"to\": 4689}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 4724, \"to\": 4729}, {\"ngram\": \"any potential negative publicity\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From RT\\u00c9 Sport, interview with the O'Donovan brothers at Rio 2016 This is why so many ofIreland's recent Olympians have been a breath of fresh airand why many of their post-event interviews have gone viral in recent years.\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4790}, {\"ngram\": \"the O'Donovan brothers\", \"from\": 4807, \"to\": 4829}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio 2016\", \"from\": 4833, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"so many ofIreland's recent Olympians\", \"from\": 4854, \"to\": 4890}, {\"ngram\": \"a breath\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 4909}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh airand\", \"from\": 4913, \"to\": 4925}, {\"ngram\": \"their 