ram\": \"the emotional interviews\", \"from\": 5341, \"to\": 5365}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting event\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Significantly more open, confident and honest, this new wave of Irish Olympians aredefying conventional expectationsto be overly subdued, excessively modest and self-effacing.\", \"from\": 5403, \"to\": 5578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5469, \"end\": 5474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9131065603736535, \"rank\": 0.05060067748159111, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this new wave\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5463}, {\"ngram\": \"conventional expectationsto\", \"from\": 5494, \"to\": 5521}, {\"ngram\": \"self-effacing\", \"from\": 5564, \"to\": 5577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hackneyed caricature of the high-achieving athletemodestly playing down expectationsfor fear of being labelled arrogant still lingers heavily in Irish sport.\", \"from\": 5579, \"to\": 5740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5730, \"end\": 5735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9131065603736535, \"rank\": 0.05060067748159111, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The hackneyed caricature\", \"from\": 5579, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"expectationsfor fear\", \"from\": 5655, \"to\": 5675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is increasingly being viewed as an old-fashioned trope in light of the new-found confidence and inspiring joy on display at recent Olympic Games by Irish athletes in their interviews.\", \"from\": 5742, \"to\": 5932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5899, \"end\": 5904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_